# ║ Path(generate_overlaps(cfg), generate overlap obligations at cfg join points) over FunctionCFG ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ generate_overlaps : FunctionCFG → List[OverlapObligat...   ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ Trusted:                                                   ║
# ║   z3.Solver.check                                          ║
